3.14.20  11:43 pm   life is ridiculous, eating is stupid; breathing is also bullshit, as is reproducing. why is everything so weird and ridiculous?
eyes are so weird. they're matter that things hit and it makes a thing reflect and plugs in to be a weird thing in your head. ears are also weird-the vibrations of the outside become a weird thing in your head. there is also a weird thing in your head making all the weird things in your head. sometimes it can make weird things from the things you see. sometimes it can make weird things out of nothing at all. thinking, knowing, imagining, believing, and feeling. these are all weird. everything is weird. and also normal. therefore normal = weird.
